.com/1oBR.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gifer.com%2F1oBR.gif&h=0c76efdf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5a2829ca6ecf4b9e62a00c57786785f6edaffe4d","tid":2403342,"uid":221490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T05:09:27.000Z","msg":"番工打卡等食飯 順便收工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6a4cf902d3d266e64940c6f30751a203482dea5","tid":2403342,"uid":33848,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T05:10:12.000Z","msg":"研究點奶"},{"pid":"9ed4d417873a8821c88402194329c07cb63082a5","tid":2403342,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T08:09:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}